    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="row no-gutters border mb-4">
            <div class="col p-4 mb-4 ">
                <p class="card-text">
                    University is a std sample application that
                    demonstrates how to use Entity Framework Core in an
                    ASP.NET Core Razor Pages web app. What is important is
                    the flow in K8.  Ingress --> University calls several 
                    WebApi pods (Redis, MQ, Identity, Longhorn(CSI), ArgoCD,
                    Prometheus, Grafana). Pod Logs can be viewed
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
