                </p>
                <p>
                    <a href="https://github.com/dfrazzitta/kubenet/blob/master/.github/workflows/docker-image1.yml" class="stretched-link">Source</a>  @*https://github.com/dotnet/AspNetCore.Docs/tree/master/aspnetcore/data/ef-rp/intro/samples" class="stretched-link">See project source code</a> *@
